# === finding-e407e06d-f369-4ab1-a6a3-8e6b42f04c77 ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:finding-e407e06d-f369-4ab1-a6a3-8e6b42f04c77> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-29T23:23:27.073126Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
